727893f-a.folder: Rockaway Beach Boule & Beach 106th Street, Queens, NY
727893f-a.text:
Rockaway Beach Boulevard, east from Beach 106th Street. At one time the Ocean Electric Railroad operated its lines on this Ave.

August 30, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
Neg # 405
